N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 466.9 - Index of interested persons

State Regulations

Persons or agencies interested in receiving notice of
proposed rule making by the State Division of Human Rights may file with the
division a written request that they be notified by mail of any proposed rule
making. The request shall specify the address to which notice is to be mailed. Such request must be renewed yearly in December. Notes
